OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry and bright
OL,6,Fmorning with spells of sunshine and
OL,7,Fthe odd shower. Sikes will become
OL,8,Fincreasingly cloudy this afternoon
OL,9,Fwith some patchy rain arriving.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average with
OL,11,Flighter winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOften cloudy this evening and
OL,14,Fovernight with further patchy rain and
OL,15,Fdrizzle, especially over the hills. A
OL,16,Fband of heavier rain then arriving
OL,17,Finto the west later. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
