OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome early brightness possible
OL,6,Fin the east, but rain in the west will
OL,7,Fspread across the country. Turning
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter throughout the
OL,9,Fafternoon with winds also gradually
OL,10,Feasing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,13,Flargely fine and dry weekend as high
OL,14,Fpressure builds in. Feeling pleasant
OL,15,Fin any sunshine and lighter winds.
OL,16,FLikely to remain similar early next
OL,17,Fweek as high pressure dominates.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
